gametitle=Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas (NTSC-U SLUS-20946 / CRC 399A49CA)
comment=Modular modern controls patch for PCSX2.
comment=Enable group 1 first. Optional modules can be toggled during play; leave group 1 enabled while the game is running.
comment=Group 2 is the universal in-vehicle D-pad/look/radio module.
comment=Group 5 enables alternate controls for cars and normal ground vehicles.
comment=Group 6 extends group 5 alternate controls to motorcycles and ATV.
comment=Group 7 extends group 5 alternate controls to boats and hovercraft.
comment=Group 8 is an Auto Fire add-on for group 5.
comment=Turreted or weaponized vehicles 407, 430, 432, 544, 564, and 601 are excluded from alternate vehicle controls so their vehicle weapon and secondary-fire controls stay closer to the stock/basic layout.
comment=Target: original NTSC-U SLUS-209.46, CRC 399A49CA.
comment=Public credit: Zeroable.

[Cheats\1 REQUIRED - Basic vehicle swap core]
description=Required core. On foot stays stock unless group 7 is enabled. In vehicles, installs the controller hook and applies the basic R2/Cross and L2/Square vehicle swap. Optional groups depend on this being enabled.
author=Zeroable + PS2 Controller Remapper by pelvicthrustman + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

