[Cheats\5 OPTIONAL - Alternate controls for cars and normal ground vehicles]
description=Requires group 1. Enables the alternate vehicle layout for cars and normal ground vehicles. Motorcycles/ATV and boats/hovercraft use the basic vehicle layout unless groups 6 and/or 7 are enabled. Turreted or weaponized vehicles 407, 430, 432, 544, 564, and 601 are excluded so their vehicle weapon and secondary-fire controls stay closer to the stock/basic layout. Enable group 2 separately for D-pad look/radio.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

// Stage-3 entry for alternate vehicle controls.
// This routes vehicle model IDs through the category chooser at FDA00.
patch=1,EE,200FD2C0,extended,0803F680
patch=1,EE,200FD2C4,extended,00000000

