[Cheats\6 OPTIONAL - Include motorcycles and ATV in alternate controls]
description=Requires groups 1 and 5. Applies group 5 alternate controls to motorcycles and the Quad/ATV. Leave this disabled if you want motorcycles and ATV to keep the basic vehicle layout.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

// Motorcycle/ATV gate.
// With this group enabled, motorcycle and ATV model IDs route to the alternate-control dispatcher.
patch=1,EE,200FDB80,extended,0803F538
patch=1,EE,200FDB84,extended,00000000

[Cheats\7 OPTIONAL - Include boats and hovercraft in alternate controls]
description=Requires groups 1 and 5. Applies group 5 alternate controls to boats and the Vortex hovercraft. Predator is excluded with the turreted/weaponized vehicles so its built-in guns stay closer to the stock/basic layout.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

// Boat/hovercraft gate.
// With this group enabled, boat and hovercraft model IDs route to the alternate-control dispatcher.
patch=1,EE,200FDB90,extended,0803F538
patch=1,EE,200FDB94,extended,00000000

[Cheats\8 OPTIONAL - Auto Fire add-on for alternate controls]
description=Requires groups 1 and 5. Changes the group 5 alternate-control dispatcher to use the Auto Fire body. R1 outputs native R2+Circle and L1 outputs native L2+Circle for vehicles routed through the alternate-control dispatcher.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

// Auto Fire dispatcher.
// With this group enabled, vehicles routed by group 5/6/7 use the Auto Fire alternate body.
patch=1,EE,200FD4E0,extended,0803F580
patch=1,EE,200FD4E4,extended,00000000

// Alternate vehicle body with Auto Fire.
