[Cheats\9 OPTIONAL - On-foot shoulder swap]
description=Requires group 1. On foot only. Shoulder swap: physical L1 outputs native L2; physical R1 outputs native R2; physical L2 outputs native L1; physical R2 outputs native R1.
author=Zeroable + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

// On-foot override.
// Group 1 uses stock controls on foot. This optional group keeps the controller hook active while on foot and routes to the on-foot shoulder-swap body.
patch=1,EE,D066BB4A,extended,02000000
patch=1,EE,205325CC,extended,0803F414
patch=1,EE,20532674,extended,0803F600

